reviewText: My grandchildren love all the Thomas The Train movies....
My Grandson LOVES Thomas and Sodor.  He loves all the videos.

Love this DVD. My Aspergers child loves the song about My Little Quackeroo
(Duck's Duck). He listens to it over & over & rocks. He loves all things Thomas including sing a longs! Thanks!
These are wonderful stories for young children. My grandson loves Cranky Bugs and asks for it very often. He knows the dialogue by heart and laughs along with the funny parts.
Teaches great life lessons. Kids can apply this to their lives
grand daughter loves them,  older grand son watched them all the time.
Our three year old granddaughter loves Thomas and friends. She especially enjoys the songs and sings along. Each story has a good message for the wee ones.
Muy son is a fan of thomas
Great viewing for kids and there's a positive life message in every video..
Grandson loves it!! And so do I!
My 2.5 yr old grandson loved it and gave it 5 stars!
Not much to say, my son loves Thomas
